uji Yamakawa)\n}}\n</center>\n\n===D-Dash Tag Team Tournament===\nThe '''D-Dash Tag Team Tournament''' was a tag team tournament held between November 3 and December 23, 2009.\n{{8TeamBracket-NoSeeds\n| RD1=Quarterfinals\n| RD2=Semifinals\n| RD3=Final\n|RD1-team1='''[[Daisuke Sasaki]] and [[Yuki Sato (wrestler)|Yuki Sato]]'''\n|RD1-team2=Satoshi Kajiwara and Amigo Suzuki\n|RD1-team3='''[[Yuji Okabayashi]] and Atsushi Ohashi'''\n|RD1-team4=Ryuichi Sekine and Kim Nam Seok\n|RD1-team5='''[[Masashi Takeda (wrestler)|Masashi Takeda]] and Takuma Obe'''\n|RD1-team6=[[Shinobu Sugawara|Shinobu]] and Taro Yamada\n|RD1-team7=Shigehiro Irie and Shun Kasagi\n|RD1-team8='''Shinya Ishikawa and Ryuichi Kawakami'''\n|RD2-team1=Daisuke Sasaki and Yuki Sato\n|RD2-team2='''Yuji Okabayashi and Atsushi Ohashi'''\n|RD2-team3=Masashi Takeda and Takuma Obe\n|RD2-team4='''Shinya Ishikawa and Ryuichi Kawakami'''\n|RD3-team1='''Yuji Okabayashi and Atsushi Ohashi'''\n|RD3-team2=Shinya Ishikawa and Ryuichi Kawakami\n}}\n\n===BJW Tag Team Championship Tournament===\nA tournament was set up for the vacant [[BJW Tag Team Championship]] after previous champions Shinya Ishikawa and Yoshihito Sasaki vacated the titles due to Ishikawa suffering a leg injury. The tournament was held between March 19 and April 28, 2010.\n<center>\n{{3RoundBracket-Byesnoseeds\n|RD1-team1='''[[Daisuke Sekimoto]] and Yoshihito Sasaki'''\n|RD1-team2=[[Abdullah Kobayashi]] and Takashi Sasaki\n|RD1-score1=Pin\n|RD1-score2=19:11\n|RD1-team5='''045 Junkies ([[Jun Kasai]] and [[Jaki Numazawa]])'''\n|RD1-team6=[[Isami Kodaka]] and [[Masashi Takeda (wrestler)|Masashi Takeda]]\n|RD1-score5=Pin\n|RD1-score6=19:46\n|RD2-team1='''Daisuke Sekimoto and Yoshihito Sasaki'''\n|RD2-team2=[[Shuji Ishikawa]] and [[Yuji Okabayashi]]\n|RD2-score1=Pin\n|RD2-score2=17:56\n|RD2-team3='''045 Junkies'''\n|RD2-team4=[[Ryuji Ito]] and [[Shadow WX]]\n|RD2-score3=Pin\n|RD2-score4=16:11\n|RD3-team1=Daisuke Sekimoto and Yoshihito Sasaki\n|RD3-team2='''045 