i<br />(11:24)   || Kazuki<br />(8:09)\n|-align=\"center\"\n! [[Shinobu Sugawara|Shinobu]]\n| Kazuki<br />(12:56) ||bgcolor=grey| X || Shinobu<br />(9:38) || Shinobu<br />(11:55) || Shinobu<br />(9:28) || Aoki<br />(7:11)\n|-align=\"center\"\n! Takuya Nomura\n| Kazuki<br />(12:35) || Shinobu<br />(9:38) ||bgcolor=grey| X || Takuya<br />(12:50) || Sakuda<br />(10:38) || Nomura<br />(7:13)\n|-align=\"center\"\n! [[Tatsuhiko Yoshino]]\n| Yoshino<br />(11:57) || Shinobu<br />(11:55) || Takuya<br />(12:50) ||bgcolor=grey| X || Yoshino<br />(9:26) || Yoshino<br />(8:02)\n|-align=\"center\"\n! Toshiyuki Sakuda\n| Kazuki<br />(11:24) || Shinobu<br />(9:28) || Sakuda<br />(10:38) || Yoshino<br />(9:26) ||bgcolor=grey| X || Sakuda<br />(9:22)\n|-align=\"center\"\n! Yuya Aoki\n| Kazuki<br />(8:09) || Aoki<br />(7:11) || Nomura<br />(7:13) || Yoshino<br />(8:02) || Sakuda<br />(9:22) ||bgcolor=grey| X\n|}\n<center>\n{{2TeamBracket\n| RD1=Final\n| RD1-seed1=\n| RD1-team1=Kazuki Hashimoto\n| RD1-seed2=\n| RD1-team2='''Shinobu'''\n| RD1-score1=Pin\n| RD1-score2=13:18\n}}\n</center>\n\n===BJW Junior Heavyweight Championship #1 Contender's Tournament===\nA tournament was set up to determine the #1 contender for [[Shinobu Sugawara|Shinobu]]'s [[BJW Junior Heavyweight Championship (2017\u2013present)|BJW Junior Heavyweight Championship]], taking place between June 13 and July 17, 2018.<ref>{{cite web |title=#1 Contender Tournament (BJW Junior Heavyweight Title)|url=https://www.wrestlingdata.com/index.php?befehl=turniere&liga=25&kategorie=201&turnier=4458|work=Wrestling Data |accessdate=24 September 2018|language=German}}</ref>\n{{8TeamBracket-NoSeeds\n| RD1=Quarterfinals\n| RD2=Semifinals\n| RD3=Final\n|RD1-team1='''Kota Sekifuda'''\n|RD1-team2=[[Tsutomu Oosugi]]\n|RD1-score1=Pin\n|RD1-score2=9:35\n|RD1-team3='''[[Kazuki Hashimoto]]'''\n|RD1-team4=Fuminori Abe\n|RD1-score3=Pin\n|RD1-score4=8:48\n|RD1-team5='''Yuya Aoki'''\n|RD1-team6=Kankuro Hoshino\n|RD1-score5=Pin\n|RD1-score6=9:04\