omoaki Honma]] and [[Ryuji Yamakawa]]\n|-\n|[[Saikyo Tag League#2000|2000]]\n|October 30, 2000\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Tokyo]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Korakuen Hall]]\n|-\n|[[Saikyo Tag League#2001|2001]]\n|September 23, 2001\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Men's Teioh]] and [[Daisuke Sekimoto]]\n|-\n|[[Saikyo Tag League#2002|2002]]\n|October 31, 2002\n|[[Yokohama]], [[Kanagawa Prefecture|Kanagawa]]\n|[[Yokohama Red Brick Warehouse]]\n|-\n|[[Saikyo Tag League#2003|2003]]\n|November 8, 2003\n|rowspan=\"9\"|Tokyo\n|rowspan=\"9\"|Korakuen Hall\n|Daikokubo Benkei and [[Abdullah Kobayashi]]\n|-\n|[[Saikyo Tag League#2009|2009]]\n|May 28, 2009\n|[[Masashi Takeda (wrestler)|Masashi Takeda]] and [[Isami Kodaka]]\n|-\n|[[Saikyo Tag League#2011|2011]]\n|November 22, 2011\n|[[Daisuke Sekimoto]] and [[Yuji Okabayashi]]\n|-\n|[[Saikyo Tag League#2012|2012]]\n|November 24, 2012\n|rowspan=\"3\"|Isami Kodaka and [[Yuko Miyamoto]]\n|-\n|[[Saikyo Tag League#2013|2013]]\n|November 22, 2013\n|-\n|[[Saikyo Tag League#2014|2014]]\n|November 21, 2014\n|-\n|[[Saikyo Tag League#2015|2015]]\n|October 29, 2015\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Daisuke Sekimoto and Yuji Okabayashi\n|-\n|[[Saikyo Tag League#2016|2016]]\n|October 31, 2016\n|-\n|[[Saikyo Tag League#2017|2017]]\n|October 15, 2017\n|[[Daichi Hashimoto]] and Hideyoshi Kamitani\n|}\n\n==Ikkitousen Deathmatch Survivor==\n{{main|Ikkitousen Deathmatch Survivor}}\nIkkitousen Deathmatch Survivor is an annual professional wrestling round-robin hardcore tournament to determine the best wrestler of BJW's deathmatch division.\n\n===Dates and venues of finals===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Event\n!Date\n!City\n!Venue\n!Winner\n|-\n|[[Ikkitousen Deathmatch Survivor#2011|2011]]\n|April 18, 2011\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Tokyo]]\n|[[Korakuen Hall]]\n|Takashi Sasaki\n|-\n|[[Ikkitousen Deathmatch Survivor#2013|2013]]\n|April 10, 2013\n|[[Shin-Kiba 1st Ring]]\n|[[Ryuji Ito]]\n|-\n|[[Ikkitousen Deathmatch Survivor#2015|2015]]\n|April 19, 2015\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Sapporo]], [[Hokkaido]]\n|Teisen Hall\n